TAX Supervisor  -
TAX Supervisor
Responsibilities
1. Prepare daily TAX Invoices2. Assist Tax Manager to ensure the validity of incoming Tax Invoice3. Input all Tax Invoices ( in and out ) daily on the system4. Prepare Tax reconciliation between monthly Tax Reports and accounting books5. Assist Tax Manager for monthly tax report submission6. Provide monthly tax reports including the tax certificates  Candidate must possess at least a Bachelor's Degree, Finance/Accountancy/Banking or equivalent.Required language(s): EnglishAt least 3 year(s) of working experience in the related field is required for this position.Preferably Supervisor / Coordinators specializing in Finance - Audit/Taxation or equivalent.Full-Time position(s) available.
